descr: Example testplan for running on a remote reference environment
descr_long: |
  Be aware, the testcases that this testplan executes is destructive, that is,
  it utilizes a block device which will be manipulated in a lot of ways.  Thus,
  provide an environment with a block-device to use for this very purpose only
  and not a block device containing your data or operating system.
hooks: [ sysinf, dmesg ]
testsuites:
  - name: exts_01
  - name: exts_02_refenv
